OL,3,CRebel Wilson memoir published with
OL,4,Credacted Sacha Baron Cohen allegations
OL,6,FRebel Wilson's headline-making memoir
OL,7,Fhas been published in the UK with
OL,8,Fallegations about the actor Sacha
OL,9,FBaron Cohen redacted for legal reasons.
OL,11,FThe book Rebel Rising, which has
OL,12,Falready been published in the US,
OL,13,Ffeatures a chapter entitled Sacha
OL,14,FBaron Cohen and Other Ass*****.
OL,16,FIn it, Wilson makes claims about Baron
OL,17,FCohen's behaviour during the filming
OL,18,Fof their 2016 comedy Grimsby, which he
OL,19,Fhas strongly denied.
