OL,6,FAfter the allegations were detailed in
OL,7,Fthe US version of the book, his
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "While we
OL,9,Fappreciate the importance of speaking
OL,10,Fout, these demonstrably false claims
OL,11,Fare directly contradicted by extensive
OL,12,Fdetailed evidence, including
OL,13,Fcontemporaneous documents, film
OL,14,Ffootage, and eyewitness accounts from
OL,15,Fthose present before, during and after
OL,16,Fthe production of The Brothers
OL,17,FGrimsby."
