OL,4,Credacted Sacha Baron Cohen allegations
OL,6,FThe Pitch Perfect and Bridesmaids star
OL,7,Fsaid she wanted to retell an
OL,8,Fexperience which made her feel
OL,9,F"completely disrespected, which led to
OL,10,Fme treating myself with even more
OL,11,Fdisrespect by eating in an extremely
OL,12,Funhealthy way".
OL,14,FIn the UK book, Wilson says she "rues
OL,15,Fthe day" she met Baron Cohen, who she
OL,16,Fdescribes as her "idol".
OL,18,FShe describes how they first met at a
OL,19,Fdinner party hosted by Little Britain
OL,20,Fstar Matt Lucas.
