OL,6,FA year later he offered her a role in
OL,7,FGrimsby, which was released in North
OL,8,FAmerica as The Brothers Grimsby, she
OL,9,Fwrites.
OL,11,FWilson played Dawn, the wife of Baron
OL,12,FCohen's character Nobby, a football
OL,13,Ffan who gets drawn into the world of
OL,14,Fhis secret agent brother.
OL,16,FShe will be discussing her book on a
OL,17,FUK tour later this month, with
OL,18,Fappearances in Edinburgh, Manchester
OL,19,Fand London.
